= Images

Image objects display images in your documents.

== Basic Image

{{img src=example.jpg}}

== Image with Alt Text

{{img src=example.jpg alt="Example Image"}}

== Image with Display Style

{{img src=example.jpg alt="Example Image" display=block}}

{{img src=example.jpg alt="Example Image" display=inline-block}}

== Image with Max Width

{{img src=example.jpg alt="Example Image" max-width=300px}}

== Image with Float

{{img src=example.jpg alt="Example Image" float=left}}

{{img src=example.jpg alt="Example Image" float=right}}

== External Image URL

{{img src=https://example.com/image.jpg alt="External Image"}}

== Image Examples

{{img src=example.jpg alt="First Image" max-width=400px}}

{{img src=example.jpg alt="Second Image" display=block max-width=500px}}

== Image in Paragraphs

This paragraph contains an image: {{img src=example.jpg alt="Icon" display=inline-block}}

== Image with Classes

{{img src=example.jpg alt="Example" class="highlight border"}}

== Image Attributes

{{img src=example.jpg alt="Example Image" display=block max-width=600px float=left class="featured-image"}}
